German Health Insurers Face Insolvency Risk, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   C h r i s   R e i t e r
-- 
2011-09-26T05:13:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/german-health-insurers-face-insolvency-risk-handelsblatt-says.html
Almost half of  Germany ’s public-
health insurers face the risk of insolvency because the system
for distributing funds doesn’t allocate enough money for sick
patients,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing a study sponsored by the
government.  To contact the reporter on this story:
